FFTE - A Fast Fourier Transform Package -


------------------------------ How to link FFTE ----------------

1) Download the package from http://www.ffte.jp
2) Expand it in this directory
3) Modify the line "FFTE_DIR = ffte_dumm" in the Makefile to the name of new directory
4) Recompile the RSDFT program with "-D_FFTE_" option ( see make.inc.org ) 


----------------------------------------------------------------

RSDFT use PZFFT3DV routine.
To compile "pzfft3dv.f", the following files are also necessary:

factor.f
fft235.f
kernel.f
pzfft3d.f
zfft3d.f
param.h


